T1  - The Canadian Women's Heart Health Alliance Atlas on the Epidemiology, Diagnosis, and Management of Cardiovascular Disease in Women - Chapter 4: Sex- and Gender-Unique Disparities: CVD Across the Lifespan of a Woman
A1  - Mulvagh S.L.
A1  - Mullen K.-A.
A1  - Nerenberg K.A.
A1  - Kirkham A.A.
A1  - Green C.R.
A1  - Dhukai A.R.
A1  - Grewal J.
