T1  - Diagnosis and classification of ileal pouch disorders: consensus guidelines from the International Ileal Pouch Consortium
A1  - Shen B.
A1  - Kochhar G.S.
A1  - Kariv R.
A1  - Liu X.
A1  - Navaneethan U.
A1  - Rubin D.T.
A1  - Cross R.K.
