T1  - PROVIDE-HF STUDY RESULTS: PATIENT-REPORTED OUTCOMES INVESTIGATION FOLLOWING INITIATION OF DRUG THERAPY WITH ENTRESTO (SACUBITRIL/VALSARTAN) IN HEART FAILURE
T3  - ACC.20 - World Congress of Cardiology. Chicago United States.
A1  - Mentz R.J.
A1  - Xu H.
A1  - O'Brien E.C.
A1  - Thomas L.
A1  - Alexy T.
