T1  - Translation and implementation of the Australian-led PCOS guideline: clinical summary and translation resources from the International Evidence-based Guideline for the Assessment and Management of Polycystic Ovary Syndrome
A1  - Teede H.J.
A1  - Misso M.L.
A1  - Boyle J.A.
A1  - Garad R.M.
A1  - McAllister V.
A1  - Downes L.
A1  - Gibson-Helm M.
