T1  - Sexual function in infertile women with polycystic ovary syndrome and unexplained infertility
A1  - Diamond M.P.
A1  - Legro R.S.
A1  - Coutifaris C.
A1  - Alvero R.
A1  - Robinson R.D.
A1  - Casson P.A.
A1  - Christman G.M.
A1  - Huang H.
A1  - Hansen K.R.
