T1  - Effect of acupuncture and clomiphene in Chinese women with polycystic ovary syndrome: A randomized clinical trial
A1  - Wu X.-K.
A1  - Stener-Victorin E.
A1  - Kuang H.-Y.
A1  - Ma H.-L.
A1  - Gao J.-S.
A1  - Xie L.-Z.
A1  - Hou L.-H.
A1  - Hu Z.-X.
A1  - Shao X.-G.
A1  - Ge J.
